&lt;i&gt;(Source: dam. (2010). In International Glossary of Hydrology Online.Retrieved May 5, 2010, from http://webworld.unesco.org/water/ihp/db/glossary/glu/EN/GF0285EN.HTM)&lt;/i&gt;</documentation>
        </annotation>
